Shanghai Jade Pearl Internet <http://www.advanced-television.com/pages/pagesb/newsarchive2/%20November%2012-19%20.html>
By Owen Hughes
Television Broadcasts, Hong Kong's largest broadcaster, has formed a joint venture in China's second-largest city, Shanghai, to provide broadband content. The venture called Shanghai Jade Pearl Internet Technologies, is aimed at Shanghai's 100,00 broadband users - a total that is expected to double in 2002. .......................
