Singer supports BBC/ITV digitisation  <http://www.advanced-television.com/pages/pagesb/newsarchive2/%20November%2012-19%20.html>
UK cableco Telewest Communications reported a 13 per cent rise on its shares by the close on Wednesday (14/11/01) after improved third-quarter core earnings - up 12 per cent and indications that it was starting to reap the benefits of bundling services together. This is its fifth consecutive quarter of financial and customer growth. .....................

